   PUBMED   10690375
REFERENCE   7  (bases 1 to 5637)
  AUTHORS   Szabo,C.I., Wagner,L.A., Francisco,L.V., Roach,J.C., Argonza,R.,
            King,M.C. and Ostrander,E.A.
  TITLE     Human, canine and murine BRCA1 genes: sequence comparison among
            species
  JOURNAL   Hum Mol Genet 5 (9), 1289-1298 (1996)
   PUBMED   8872468
  REMARK    GeneRIF: The amino terminal RING finger motif and the granin
            consensus sequence are conserved between human, canine, and murine
            BRCA1 genes.
